課程概述 Course Description
       就管理的觀點，數量方法論(Quantative Methodology)乃以管理數學與計量為據，對企業經營所面對經濟現象或管理問題，透過邏輯推理加以驗證與分析的一套科學。在企業管理的領域，數量方法的探討大致集中於(1)作業研究OR(2)系統分析或系統模擬，System Analysis of Simulation及(3)計量經濟分析(Econometric Analysis)。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Realize more details about data miningLearn to analyze the data with different quantitative perspectives Learn the operation of SAS and SPSS 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction & Syllabus2Introduction3Getting to Know Your Data4Getting to Know Your Data5Data Processing6OFF7Data Warehousing and Online Analytical Processing 8Data Warehousing and Online Analytical Processing 9Data Cube Technology10Data Cube Technology11Mining Frequent Patterns, Associations, and Correlations12Mining Frequent Patterns, Associations, and Correlations13Presentation 114Presentation 215Presentation 316OFF17Presentation 418Final Exam 

